>\n<br />\n屌佢老母咩, <br />\n就算係表達政治意見, 都係言論自由<br />\n難道佢地今年搞既跨性別主題就唔係政治咩？<br />\n死奶共狗黎"},{"pid":"4f118d42dac88530865fb6ec9c543a457c2a0216","tid":896314,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近年香港發生了不同的政治禁絕事件，但政治禁區具體範圍從來沒有人真正知道，因為散播恐懼以達到控制的要點就是不要清楚地說明，讓人們自行猜想，作繭自縛。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本就唔需要「清楚地說明」<br />\n因為根本就唔應該有所謂「政治禁區」<br />\n政治意見表達自由係由法律及國際公約保障架, <br />\n你去求殖民政府「清楚地說明政治禁區」, 然後自己寒嬋唔去觸及禁區<br />\n咪即你自己合理化設立所謂「政治禁區」囉<br />\n你自己咪作繭自縛囉, <br />\n呀大作家韓麗珠！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbb6d7ca992e15a41e4941764d1479622d63d0e","tid":896314,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:36:22.000Z","msg":"任何人係文學節演講, 都可以促成政治利益 / 商業利益 / 個人利益架<br />\n<br />\n你CUT撚晒演講啦<br />\n<br />\n甚至本書入到文學節 都可以促成政治利益 / 商業利益 / 個人利益架<br />\n<br />\n直頭唔會做啦, 正仆街黎"},{"pid":"58a2edc53153991f0ed37d918d630cfe1f07062f","tid":896314,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e77958f15d129f435d592f62240fd739daf39ca","tid":896314,"uid":125542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:37:35.000Z","msg":"曲線支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfc4a82f1ae2ac8f821b505e1def771e695184a","tid":896314,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/QVGhwG8k/MA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FQVGhwG8k%2FMA.jpg&h=9c3bd2ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5910735063cf1f17c2b17326d2d51b94585c2e8f","tid":896314,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/QVGhwG8k/MA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FQVGhwG8k%2FMA.jpg&h=9c3bd2ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b5528296c816e3b9fe2351706015da9d00d266e","tid":896314,"uid":3520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T08:58:13.000Z","msg":"BNO??<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e147b2a072efe28240c010f054828637257630","tid":896314,"uid":12704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:51:38.000Z","msg":"唔係話永久居民唔可以被拒入境咩<br />\n用BC反而會有機會唔俾入"},{"pid":"1c27a00c49e9c6835c57e7d4d149813b0e53a4f5","tid":896314,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係話永久居民唔可以被拒入境咩<br />\n用BC反而會有機會唔俾入</blockquote><br />\n即刻捉去九龍站"},{"pid":"e70ee51ea265e4c6f52067b62e57a658263b151c","tid":896314,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31e147b2a072efe28240c010f054828637257630","tid":896314,"uid":12704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T10:51:38.000Z","msg":"唔係話永久居民唔可以被拒入境咩<br />\n用BC反而會有機會唔俾入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T11:07:59.000Z","msg":"佢都有香港永久居民身份証<br />\n正常用到E道入就唔會用BC入既"}]}